nodes.keybinds:
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------
# KEYBINDINGS KEYBINDS CONFIG
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------
# - keys: keybind keys combination (array of items from "_keys.yml" file; max 2)
#   desc: keybind description (string)
#   tags: keybind tags (array of items from "tags.yml" file)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------

- keys: ["W"]
  desc: "Movement"
  tags: ["general", "vehicle"]
- keys: ["A"]
  desc: "Movement"
  tags: ["general", "vehicle"]
- keys: ["S"]
  desc: "Movement"
  tags: ["general", "vehicle"]
- keys: ["D"]
  desc: "Movement"
  tags: ["general", "vehicle"]
- keys: ["CTRL"]
  desc: "Crouch"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["SHIFT"]
  desc: "Sprint"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["E"]
  desc: "Interaction"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["T"]
  desc: "Chat"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["Y"]
  desc: "Player IDs"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["1"]
  desc: "Quick Slot"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["2"]
  desc: "Quick Slot"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["3"]
  desc: "Quick Slot"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["4"]
  desc: "Quick Slot"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["5"]
  desc: "Quick Slot"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["U"]
  desc: "Vehicle lock"
  tags: ["general", "vehicle"]
- keys: ["F"]
  desc: "Enter/exit vehicle"
  tags: ["general", "vehicle"]
- keys: ["G"]
  desc: "Glovebox"
  tags: ["vehicle"]
- keys: ["Z"]
  desc: "Radial menu"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["X"]
  desc: "Hands up animation"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["C"]
  desc: "Look behind"
  tags: ["general", "vehicle"]
- keys: ["V"]
  desc: "Change camera"
  tags: ["general", "vehicle"]
- keys: ["B"]
  desc: "Point at animation"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["B"]
  desc: "Seatbelt"
  tags: ["vehicle"]
- keys:  ["F1"]
  desc: "Voice volume"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["F5"]
  desc: "Command job menu"
  tags: ["jobs"]
- keys: ["F6"]
  desc: "Job menu"

- keys: ["F7"]

- keys: ["F8"]

- keys: ["F10"]

  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["TAB"]

  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["CAPS LOCK"]
  desc: "Radio"
  tags: ["general"]
- keys: ["ALT", "W"]

  tags: ["vehicle"]
- keys: ["ALT", "UP"]
  desc: "Panic button"
  tags: ["police"]
- keys: ["SHIFT", "UP"]
  desc: "Handcuff"
  tags: ["police"]
- keys: ["SHIFT", "DOWN"]

- keys: ["SHIFT", "LEFT"]

- keys: ["SHIFT", "RIGHT"]

nodes.tags:
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------
# KEYBINDINGS TAGS CONFIG
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------
# - tag: tag name (string)
#   label: tag title (string)
#   default: tag enabled by default (boolean)
#   color: tag color (string; optional; any valid CSS color)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------

- tag: "general"
  label: "General"
  default: true
- tag: "vehicle"
  label: "Vehicle"
  default: true
  color: "#9e8bf9"
- tag: "jobs"
  label: "Jobs"
  default: true
  color: "#fda739"
- tag: "police"
  label: "Police/EMS"
  default: false
  color: "#4283f4"
